{"tid":313934,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[超突發多圖性愛血腥裸露慎入]今鋪一定比人燒春袋","createTime":"2017-07-08T17:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T07:35:14.000Z","uid":1858,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"946713d02a1d00dd6568fcc9b4af28c45afc2ce9","tid":313934,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T17:53:28.000Z","msg":"話說頭先入廚房洗杯都冇咩為意有冇甲由，驟眼睇水平線又冇咩野，但係平時呢個鐘數實冇一兩隻，點知當我一抬頭望竟然比我見到兩隻甲由一絲不掛咁扑緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/011818_1b2e63e18b32bfb6e236e270ba9384cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F011818_1b2e63e18b32bfb6e236e270ba9384cd.jpg&h=08ab2f35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/011819_1b2e63e18b32bfb6e236e270ba9384cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F011819_1b2e63e18b32bfb6e236e270ba9384cd.jpg&h=e0bcbf94&s={SIZE}\" />仆你個臭街係我地頭扑野 ，我緊係一手執起份厚報紙就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">殺</span></span>啦，我手起報落第一下miss大嚇到佢地，點知比我發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來甲由扑緊野個時個身係痴撚住左，即係好似平時男人條撚插左入女人個閪到，而唔係蜻蜓點水咁點就算，所以當我撻q嚇到佢地個時，佢地兩隻一齊痴住跌落地。最後唔講咁多，去圖<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/012318_ada117cb6cca4967c486d6aceb9a70fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F012318_ada117cb6cca4967c486d6aceb9a70fe.jpg&h=62d781f8&s={SIZE}\" />死就應該未死，所以我諗住放佢地係到典到聽朝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外附上小嘍囉一隻<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/012437_208f75db8e0c31d0ca013f1258166a4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F012437_208f75db8e0c31d0ca013f1258166a4d.jpg&h=d56b2770&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/012438_208f75db8e0c31d0ca013f1258166a4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F012438_208f75db8e0c31d0ca013f1258166a4d.jpg&h=0de642d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/012438_a56354d469f2d68a10b3002768177ede.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F012438_a56354d469f2d68a10b3002768177ede.jpg&h=bfa072a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同樣係未死，都係由佢典多陣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a62d3968aa1cd329261f6226516189ea97e091","tid":313934,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00458d10bd3e8446d8f6c92d16014f6ff00001e6","tid":313934,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:04:09.000Z","msg":"地板甲由扑野上方有滴白色液體<br />\n樓主係咪忍唔住打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd0d8d94b030b978329e99c95ae4410e9ef23f7","tid":313934,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:10:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地板甲由扑野上方有滴白色液體<br />\n樓主係咪忍唔住打J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個畫面咁難得，你估下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12d12a5c6c1784f6d66ef892b1a1af1f532fa6d","tid":313934,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T18:47:12.000Z","msg":